Image 1 of 3 showing our ray tracer handles falloff for point lights.

This image is of a green sphere with a specular component that reflects blue light.  There sphere is centered at the origin with a radius of 0.65.  It is under a white point light at (2,2,2) with no falloff.  The rendered sphere looks exactly the sphere created by input-08.  

Time to render: less than 1 second.